value.0: Dogma of Bahgtru: The only true calling for an orc is battle. Kill as many opponents as possible, for one is measured by the number and power of those one has dispatched. Make no plans before or during battle, for plans are for those too weak to succeed by mere force of arms alone. Trust in one's strength and Bahgtru will reward one with dominion over others. By weeding out the weak, the warriors of Bahgtru ensure that only the strongest survive to produce the next generation.
